Interface IBaselineSet

All Superinterfaces:
IBaselineSetHandle, IItem, IItemHandle, IManagedItem, IManagedItemHandle, ISimpleItem, ISimpleItemHandle
public interface IBaselineSet
extends ISimpleItem, IBaselineSetHandle

A BaselineSet represents an immutable collection of baselines.

Feature access profile values:

  • name: SMALL
  • comment: DEFAULT
  • baselines: DEFAULT

Since:
0.5

getBaselines

java.util.List getBaselines()
Returns the list of IBaselineHandles captured by this set. The returned list is guaranteed to have baselines from different components. There are no overlapping component baselines.

Returns:
the list (never empty) of baselines captured by this sets (element type: IBaselineHandle); the list is immutable; never null
